Security Suite — combined license
==================================

Security Suite is an aggregate work that bundles material from several upstream
projects and adds original content. Different parts carry different licenses. This
file explains the overall position; the full text of every upstream license is in the
`licenses/` directory, and `NOTICE.md` lists exactly which component came from where.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Original content in this package — MIT License
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The following parts are original to this distribution and are released under the MIT
License (below): the unified marketplace/plugin manifests, the full-codebase scan
framework (`security-suite/scripts/security-scan.sh`), the `security-audit`,
`sast-scanning`, `recon-automation`, and `dependency-security` skills, the
`/security-scan` command, and the README/NOTICE documentation.

