--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. Wrapped (NOT bundled) external tools — their own licenses
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
These tools are NOT redistributed in this package. The wrapper skills install them
from their own upstream sources at runtime, where they are governed by their own
licenses:

  - ReconForge  — MIT License        © 2026 ferasbusiness666   licenses/ReconForge-MIT.txt
  - MEDUSA      — GNU AGPL-3.0        © Pantheon-Security       licenses/medusa-AGPL-3.0.txt

Because no MEDUSA source code is included here, this aggregate is not a derivative of
MEDUSA and the AGPL-3.0 copyleft does not extend to this package. When a user installs
MEDUSA (e.g. `pip install medusa-security`) they receive it directly from its authors
under AGPL-3.0 and must comply with that license in their own use.

